character.name: Tsuki
character.description: 17 years old, male, full name Lunerisson "Tsuki" Kiyomasu. I play the guitar. I'm docile, polite, spunky, light-hearted and with a sense of humor, but rather timid and awkward with social interaction. especially with the opposite gender. I can get pretty cocky and do some wisecracking jokes at times, but my heroic side is more apparent. I like gaming in general, tech from the late 90s to the early 2000s and Skate Punk music.
